<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=5040&amp;p=45444#p45444"><![CDATA[
Dwedit, you want to confuse the guy? But yeah, if a program sets the vertical scroll to values larger than 239 the PPU will render the attribute table as if it were part of the name table. This is very rare though, and the few games that did this show garbage at the areas where this happens.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=95">tokumaru</a> — Thu Apr 09, 2009 10:28 pm</p><hr />
