I think they are used if you set the scroll range out of bounds and force it to draw the attribute tables.  So you can make all BG palettes the same color, and get 16 extra scrolling pixels if you want to do things the weird way.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=53">Dwedit</a> — Thu Apr 09, 2009 5:44 pm</p><hr />
